original_title: Return to Staxus International College: Part 1
overview: Our guys are back to college in this new second season! After the first one we will discover secrets, drama, romance and lots of sex! How is Craig going to pay for what he's looking for? What happened to Trent after the pool? What is Nathan going to do in the bathroom with Angel? Get your pencils ready... if you know what I mean by pencils!
title: Return to Staxus International College: Part 1
